"It's described as scaling and erythematous, which means it's red and scaly.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.050287,0.067272,0.080555,0.093804,0.10162,0.10425,0.10369,0.097098,0.093745,0.090808,0.073257,0.043616],"unified_progress":[0.052802,0.073712,0.085929,0.09669,0.09863,0.10026,0.097486,0.094751,0.090171,0.08158,0.069781,0.058207]},{"section":16,"text":"That sounds like a skin issue, possibly related to the medication.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030126,0.070351,0.090569,0.10478,0.10912,0.11052,0.10763,0.099311,0.092132,0.084298,0.065769,0.035394],"unified_progress":[0.037585,0.074243,0.092695,0.10255,0.1049,0.10135,0.10351,0.096233,0.090162,0.0826,0.067479,0.046685]},{"section":17,"text":"Could it be a reaction to one of the drugs?","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.026329,0.054911,0.078153,0.096082,0.10464,0.11003,0.11143,0.10831,0.10149,0.095075,0.073682,0.039876],"unified_progress":[0.035478,0.068601,0.086019,0.0968,0.099986,0.09941,0.10132,0.1006,0.094998,0.09193,0.073832,0.051033]},{"section":18,"text":"Hydralazine can cause rashes, so that fits.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.028393,0.047925,0.062935,0.076208,0.087561,0.098828,0.10854,0.11389,0.11832,0.11714,0.090531,0.049732],"unified_progress":[0.037425,0.061976,0.079156,0.088567,0.096916,0.10081,0.10131,0.10195,0.098006,0.095067,0.080262,0.058553]},{"section":19,"text":"But hang on, there's more to consider.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.11289,0.089568,0.084105,0.076083,0.077684,0.080088,0.083408,0.092071,0.083488,0.056599,0.05562,0.10839],"unified_progress":[0.2068,0.077884,0.065619,0.065628,0.074908,0.075005,0.095052,0.083858,0.080159,0.063893,0.057269,0.053929]},{"section":20,"text":"Furosemide can cause hyperuricemia, leading to gout.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.033638,0.052754,0.068548,0.084485,0.093955,0.10399,0.1108,0.11005,0.11073,0.11158,0.079372,0.040087],"unified_progress":[0.041247,0.071954,0.066405,0.10018,0.10759,0.10399,0.10414,0.10314,0.095521,0.087565,0.069389,0.048876]},{"section":21,"text":"Gout often causes joint pain and sometimes a rash if there are tophi.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.025218,0.039625,0.05327,0.067665,0.082078,0.095406,0.10769,0.11296,0.12007,0.12809,0.10679,0.061145],"unified_progress":[0.034359,0.058142,0.077431,0.089284,0.097229,0.10809,0.10443,0.10288,0.099105,0.093283,0.077645,0.05812]},{"section":22,"text":"Tophi are those little deposits under the skin that can look like nodules.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.022759,0.038112,0.05293,0.069213,0.08531,0.10032,0.11324,0.11782,0.12444,0.13131,0.097424,0.047121],"unified_progress":[0.032232,0.057694,0.079798,0.092736,0.099988,0.10878,0.10733,0.104,0.098382,0.090934,0.073237,0.054888]},{"section":23,"text":"So, maybe that's part of what's going on here?","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.02365,0.043824,0.058293,0.070628,0.080793,0.091787,0.10168,0.10953,0.11665,0.11816,0.10794,0.077063],"unified_progress":[0.034401,0.058817,0.07378,0.083299,0.091536,0.095432,0.097245,0.10058,0.099631,0.10136,0.090099,0.073825]},{"section":24,"text":"Also, the fever could be a clue.","dimension":1,"group":4,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018833,0.047816,0.066066,0.080371,0.089862,0.098844,0.10587,0.11161,0.11558,0.11597,0.09554,0.05363],"unified_progress":[0.031372,0.062656,0.078631,0.08912,0.095958,0.097535,0.10164,0.1015,0.09995,0.099998,0.084147,0.057485]},{"section":25,"text":"If she's got a fever along with the joint pain and rash, it makes me think of an inflammatory process.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.021016,0.046504,0.065241,0.08067,0.090102,0.098533,0.10461,0.10639,0.10682,0.11099,0.10338,0.065745],"unified_progr